Jay O. Sanders https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jay_O._Sanders 0 Jay Olcutt Sanders (born April 16, 1953) is an American actor who has worked in theatre, film, and TV, known for JFK (1991). He frequently appears in plays Off-Broadway at The Public Theatre.
